     calculated                        1,954        1,509        29%
    ------------------------           -----        -----        ---

    Total Silver Produced (oz)
     calculated                      386,002      380,620         1%
    --------------------------       -------      -------        ---

    Total Copper Produced (Lbs)
     calculated                    1,133,161    1,054,935         7%
