                Avino Silver & Gold Mines Ltd. engages in mining and exploration activities. It focuses in silver reserves in Durango region of North Central Mexico. It operates through the Mexico Exploration and Evaluation Assets, and Canada Exploration and Evaluation Assets segments. The company was founded on May 15, 1968 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
            




