Avino Mine
Exploration


Ana Maria
El Hueco
Aranjuez
El Laberinto (Jabali)

Canada

Bralorne Gold Mine
Eagle Property
Minto Property
Olympic Property

Recent Photos





Overview





Operating in Canada and Mexico, Avino holds two producing precious metals projects plus another in trial production. The company also maintains a diversified pipeline of gold, silver and base metals exploration properties. With the exception of the Avino mine, which is owned 99.28%, all the company's properties are owned 100%.


Avino PropertyDurango State, Mexico
Bralorne PropertyBritish Columbia, Canada
Minto PropertyBritish Columbia, Canada
Olympic-Kelvin PropertyBritish Columbia, Canada
Eagle PropertyYukon Territory, Canada


 
















